<item>
 <title>Beyond Linux: Changing the World with Open Source</title>
 <link>https://www.socallinuxexpo.org/scale9x/presentations/beyond-linux-changing-world-open-source</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;At opensource.com, we explore what happens when the open source way is applied to the world. What problems can we solve? How would it affect the way we learn? Run our businesses? Our governments?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-track&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                &lt;a href=&quot;category/presentationcategory/general&quot;&gt;General&lt;/a&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-presentation-short-abs&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;“Open source” has become more than a way to describe software source code and the collaborative model for how it&#039;s developed. It&#039;s now a business model, an education model, and the future of government and law. It&#039;s changing our lives through its principles: openness, transparency, collaboration, diversity, and rapid prototyping. Learn about what others have been doing, and get involved!&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-presentation-speaker-id&quot;&gt;
